Oh bum. I had it that way originally, for that reason, then left for a while, wondered what I was doing and removed the 'superflous' bit.
+#if defined(CONFIG_ISAPNP) || (defined (MODULE) && defined (CONFIG_ISAPNP_MODULE))
Matthew Bell
