> > module.
> 
> > --- linux-2.4.19.orig/drivers/net/3c515.c       2002-02-25 19:37:59.000000000 +0000
> > +++ linux-2.4.19/drivers/net/3c515.c    2002-08-03 18:24:05.000000000 +0100
